Description: asyncio-friendly MySQL driver (Avalan PPA pin)
 aiomysql is an asyncio bridge in front of the PyMySQL wire-protocol
 implementation, exposing async cursors and connection pools. Noble
 ships 0.1.1 (below floor) and Debian sid ships 0.3.2 (above ceiling);
 this rebuild pins 0.2.0 to satisfy Avalan's `>= 0.2, < 0.3` window.
 The optional `[sa]` extra (sqlalchemy < 1.4) is not declared here --
 callers depend on Avalan's PPA python3-sqlalchemy 2.x instead.
